gate: OPEN
task: S74-TD6
title: Fix Track Selection Execute Hang
description: |
  Investigate and fix the app hang when clicking execute on track selection:
  - Find where track selection, display, color, and width controls are implemented
  - Identify the cause of the hang when execute is pressed
  - Check for infinite loops, blocking operations, or memory issues
  - Ensure the UI matches the history screen design
  - Fix the track rendering with proper color and width

acceptance:
  - Execute button no longer hangs the application
  - Track selection works properly
  - Track display shows correctly with chosen color and width
  - UI matches history screen design
  - No console errors or performance issues

requires: []
estimated: 3 hours
